# Literature sources — original article PDFs are kept LOCAL ONLY.
# Publisher PDFs are copyrighted and must not be redistributed in a public
# repository. The public record is the findings notes under docs/literature/notes/,
# not the source documents. See docs/literature/sources/README.md.
docs/literature/sources/**
!docs/literature/sources/README.md
# Belt-and-braces: never commit a PDF from anywhere in the literature area.
docs/literature/**/*.pdf
